IN RE: T.T.E. 238A18-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 14, 2019 Michelle F. Lynch, Attorney at Law, for T.T.E. Janelle E. Varley, Assistant Attorney General, Todd Williams, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

Amended

The following order has been entered on the Motion for Extension of Time to File Brief filed on the 14th of January 2019 by Juvenile:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th of January 2019."

Juvenile shall have up to and including the 27th day of February 2019 to file and serve his/her brief with this Court.
